<h3><a name="languages">What languages do you support?</a></h3>

<p>Presently, we only support English, but we would like to add more languages for the notifications, as well as for the website.  If you would like to help with this please let us know.</p>

<h3><a name="howmuch">How much does Recollect cost?</a></h3> 
 
<p>For a basic service... it's free!</p> 
 
<p>We offer email, twitter and developer reminders, as well as an ical download of your city's garbage schedule for free.</p> 
 
<p>If you'd like to get a voice phone call or a text message reminder we charge $6 for 3 months of service.  All fees are in Canadian dollars.</p> 

<h3><a name="friendbuy">Can I buy Recollect for a friend or family member?</a></h3>

<p>Yes! Given we are a small start up we hope that web savvy friends will buy SMS and phone reminders for their less web savvy and forgetful friends! Or perhaps a gift from real-estate agents for new home owners. One note, please be sure that you have asked their permission before buying. 
We view sending some one an unsolicited reminder very seriously and will terminate service - without a refund - if we receive a complaint.</p>

